# HardCarry

Simple API for the League based, IMDB inspired website.

## API Root [/]

### Retrieve the API Entry Points [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            'urls': {
                        "champions_url": "/champions",
                        "abilities_url": "/abilities",
                        "summoners_url": "/summoners",
                        "featured-games_url": "/featured-games",
                        "search_url": "/search"
                    }
        }
    
# Group Featured Games

Featured Games are recent or current matches that typically feature skilled players.
They have the following attributes:

### Attributes
* id: (integer) ID of the featured game.
* champions: (dictionary) All the information for the champions used in the game.
* gameLength: (integer) Amount of time in seconds passed since the game started.
* game_mode: (string) Game mode (CLASSIC, ODIN, ARAM, TUTORIAL, ONEFORALL, ASCENSION, FIRSTBLOOD, KINGPORO)
* game_type: (string) Game type (CUSTOM_GAME, MATCHED_GAME, TUTORIAL_GAME)
* mapId: (integer) ID of the map the game is being played on.
* summoners: (dictionary) All the information for the summoners who played the game.

