# Group Champions

Champions are playable characters with unique abilities.
They have the following attributes:

### Attributes

* abilities: (dictionary) All the abilities belonging to this champion.
* summoners: (dictionary) All summoners who have played this champion.
* featured_games: (dictionary) All featured games this champion has been played in.
* name: (string) Name of the champion.
* allytips: (blob) Tips for allies.
* enemytips: (blob) Tips for enemies.
* championId: (integer) ID of the champion.
* imageFileName: (string) Filename of this champion's image.
* lore: (string) Description of this champion's background lore.
* partype: (string) Champion type.
* title: (string) Champion's title.
* attack: (integer) Champion's attack rating.
* defense: (integer) Champion's defense rating.
* magic: (integer) Champion's magic rating.
* difficulty: (integer) Champion's difficulty rating.
* passiveDescription: (string) Description of passive abilities.
* passiveImageFileName: (string) Filename of this champion's passive ability image.
* passiveName: (string) Champion's passive ability name.
* armor: (double) Armor stat.
* armorperlevel: (double) Armor stat increase per level.
* attackdamage: (double) Attack damage stat.
* attackdamageperlevel: (double) Attack damage stat increase per level.
* attackrange: (double) Attack range stat.
* attackspeedoffset: (double) Attack speed offset (from items or abilities that also increase speed).
* attackspeedperlevel: (double) Attack speed offset increase per level.
* crit: (double) Chance of critical hit.
* critperlevel: (double) Increase in chance of critical hit per level.
* hp: (double) Health points.
* hpperlevel: (double) Increase in HP per level.
* hpregen: (double) HP regeneration stat.
* hpregenperlevel: (double) Increase in HP regeneration per level.
* movespeed: (double) Speed of movement.
* mp: (double) Magic points.
* mpperlevel: (double) Increase in MP per level.
* mpregen: (double) MP regeneration stat.
* mpregenperlevel: (double) Increase in MP regeneration per level.
* spellblock: (double) The resistence to magic damage.
* spellblockperlevel: (double) Increase in resistence to magic damage per level.
* numberOfSkins: (integer) Number of skins belonging to this champion.
* youtube: (string) Link to YouTube video of this champion.

