# Group Abilities

Abilities are the moves available to Champions.
They have the following attributes:

### Attributes
* description: (string) Description of the spell.
* costType: (string) Type of cost of this spell.
* id: (integer) Spell ID.
* imageFileName: (string) Spell's image filename.
* maxrank: (integer) Maximum rank to level up for this spell.
* name: (string) Name of spell.
* tooltip: (string) A tip for using this spell.
* championId: (integer) ID of champion who can cast this spell.

