# Group Summoners

Summoners are human players who compete in Featured Games.
They have the following attributes:

### Attributes
* champions: (dictionary) Champions used by this summoner.
* featured_games: (dictionary) Games this summoner has played in.
* summoner_id: (integer) ID of the summoner.
* name: (string) Name of the summoner.
* profileIconId: (integer) ID of the icon associated with the summoner.
* summonerLevel: (integer) Summoner level associated with the summoner.
* bot: (boolean) Indicates whether the summoner is a bot or human.
* championId: (integer) ID of the champion this summoner is using.
* teamId: (integer) ID of the team this summoner is on.

